JOB MC_SIMULATION     submit_files/simulate.submit
SCRIPT PRE MC_SIMULATION executables/delete_simulations.sh
SCRIPT PRE MC_SIMULATION src/update_simulate_submit.py
RETRY MC_SIMULATION 2

JOB TIME_RESIDUALS    submit_files/time_residuals.submit
RETRY TIME_RESIDUALS 2

JOB SELECT_PARAMETERS submit_files/select_parameters.submit
RETRY SELECT_PARAMETERS 2


PARENT MC_SIMULATION CHILD TIME_RESIDUALS
PARENT TIME_RESIDUALS CHILD SELECT_PARAMETERS

